all|1988\u201389]]\n|Second Division\n|44||4||2||0||3||0||2||0||51||4\n|-\n|[[1989\u201390 in English football|1989\u201390]]\n|Second Division\n|7||0||0||0||2||0||2||0||11||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!51!!4!!2!!0!!5!!0!!4!!0!!62!!4\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[Stoke City F.C.|Stoke City]]\n|[[1989\u201390 Stoke City F.C. season|1989\u201390]]\n|Second Division\n|18||0||0||0||0||0||0||0||18||0\n|-\n|[[1990\u201391 Stoke City F.C. season|1990\u201391]]\n|[[Football League Third Division|Third Division]]\n|44||3||3||0||4||0||1||0||52||3\n|-\n|[[1991\u201392 Stoke City F.C. season|1991\u201392]]\n|[[Football League Third Division|Third Division]]\n|13||0||1||0||2||0||4||0||20||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!75!!3!!4!!0!!6!!0!!5!!0!!90!!3\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[Bradford City A.F.C.|Bradford City]]\n|[[1991\u201392 in English football|1991\u201392]]\n|Third Division\n|6||0||0||0||0||0||0||0||6||0\n|-\n|[[1992\u201393 in English football|1992\u201393]]\n|Second Division\n|32||3||3||1||2||0||3||0||40||3\n|-\n|[[1993\u201394 in English football|1993\u201394]]\n|Second Division\n|7||0||2||0||1||0||1||0||11||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!45!!3!!5!!1!!3!!0!!4!!0!!57!!3\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[Dundee F.C.|Dundee]]\n|[[1993\u201394 in Scottish football|1993\u201394]]\n|[[Scottish Football League Premier Division|Scottish Premier Division]]\n|||||||||||||||||||\n|-\n|[[1994\u201395 in Scottish football|1994\u201395]]\n|[[Scottish Football League First Division|Scottish First Division]]\n|||||||||||||||||||\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!54!!2!!5!!0!!2!!0!!3!!0!!64!!2\n|-\n|rowspan=\"7\"|[[Exeter City F.C.|Exeter City]]\n|[[1995\u201396 in English football|1995\u201396]]\n|Third Division\n|44||2||1||0||2||0||0||0||47||2\n|-\n|[[1996\u201397 in English football|1996\u201397]]\n|Third Division\n|46||6||2||0||2||0||2||0||52||6\n|-\n|[[1997\u201398 in English football|1997\u201398]]\n|Third Division\n|38||1||2||0||2||0||1||0||43||1\n|-\n|[[1998\u201399 in English football|1998\u201399]]\n|Third D